#: '''thar {{l|ga|an}} {{l|ga|doras}}''' -- ''[[through]] the [[door]]''
# [[beyond]]
#: '''thar [[mo#Irish|m]]'{{l|ga|eolas}}''' -- ''[[beyond]] [[my]] [[knowledge]]''

